** {{Bgcolortext|down|Bottom 4 teams}} from each group are eliminated.

* '''Quarter Finals:''''' July 30th - August 1st, 2025
** 48 teams, 3 matchdays.
** Teams are divided into 3 groups of 16 teams each.
** Each team plays a total of 6 matches.
** {{Bgcolortext|up|Top 8 teams}} from each group advance to ''Semi Finals.
** {{Bgcolortext|down|Bottom 8 teams}} from each group are eliminated.

* '''Semi Finals:''''' Aug 2nd - 3rd, 2025
** 24 teams, 2 matchdays.
** Teams are divided into 3 groups of 8 teams each.
** Each team plays a total of 8 matches.
** {{Bgcolortext|up|Top 16 teams}} from the overall standings qualify for ''Grand Finals.
** {{Bgcolortext|down|Bottom 8 teams}} are eliminated.

* '''Grand Finals''' - ''Aug 4th - 5th, 2025
** 16 teams, 2 matchdays.
** 18 matches (9 each day).

